text: Assalé Molo Hilaire is an Ivorian former professional footballer who is last known to have been under contract to Manaw Myay of the Myanmar National League. ==Early life== Influenced by Brazilian footballer Ronaldo and Ivorian Aruna Dindane after watching them play, Hilaire started football aged 7 and aimed to turn professional despite no support from his father.Assale Hilaire : Je veux terminer meilleur butter Talentcache.ci ==Myanmar== After beginning with the Myanmar National League's Yadanarbon in 2010-11, Hilaire switched to Manaw Myay in 2012,Assale Molo Hilaire : La Nouvelle Coqueluche Du Manaw Myay FC Talentcache.ci bagging 15 goals and finishing as 5th on the scoring charts that season.Assale Molo Hilaire : Ue Saison Tout Feu Tout Flamme !!! Talentcache.ci Extending his contract for another year,Manaw Myay FC (1ère division Birmane) : Hilaire Assale Ne Partita Pas Talentcache.ci the Ivorian forward targeted the top-scorer award for 2013, bagging 13 goals by early July that year.Birmanie : Hilaire Assalé, puissance 13 !
